Package: proxyr
Title: Proxy Configuration and Credential Management
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Russell", "Politzky", email = "russell.politzky@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Gemini", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides tools to manage proxy settings and credentials in R. Supports temporary proxy configuration via `with_proxy`, secure credential storage using the `keyring` package, and automatic Windows system proxy detection.
